AN ACT
To authorize the conveyance of certain state property.
Be it enacted by the General Assembly of the state of Missouri, as follows:
Section 1. 1. The governor is hereby authorized and empowered to sell, transfer,
2 grant, convey, remise, release, and forever quitclaim all interest of the state of Missouri
3 in property located in Cole County, Missouri, to the City of Jefferson. The property to
4 be conveyed is more particularly described as follows:
